================================================================================
                                  Requirements
================================================================================

Build tools
===========

    * gcc (>= 4.7)
        http://gcc.gnu.org

    * CMake (>= v2.6)
        http://www.cmake.org

    * C++ Boost Libraries (>= v1.44)
        http://www.boost.org

    * Broccoli (>= v1.4)
        http://www.bro-ids.org

Optional
========

    * Google perftools (version >= 1.0)
        http://code.google.com/p/google-perftools

    * Doxygen (version >= 1.5.9)
        http://www.doxygen.org


================================================================================
                                  Installation
================================================================================

VAST ships with autotools-like wrapper scripts to control the build process.
See

    ./configure --help

for available configuration options. By default, the build process creates a
directory "build" in which the compilation takes place. After configuring, you
kick off the compilation with

    make

and install VAST with

    make install

================================================================================
